Package: windcut
Title: Weather Time Series Feature Engineering for Plant Disease Epidemiology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kaique S.",
           family = "Alves",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kaique.alves@example.com")
Description: Tools for transforming weather time series into model-ready
    features for plant disease epidemiology. The package emphasizes
    relative-time window analysis, allowing users to scan candidate
    time windows around biological reference dates and compute biologically
    interpretable weather summaries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/AlvesKS/windcut, https://alvesks.github.io/windcut/
